# Parameterised Human Behaviour for Safety Filter Evaluation

## Goal
Show safety filter **generalises across diverse human behaviours** using **SMPL-H** (52 joints, native AMASS format).

This is implemented as a **wrapper package** (`safety_bigym`) around the existing `bigym` package.

---

## Architecture

```
HumanBehaviourSampler.sample_scenario(seed)  ← called on env.reset()
        │
        ▼
MotionController
  ├─ t < trigger: AMASS playback
  ├─ trigger ≤ t < trigger+blend: interpolate AMASS↔IK
  └─ t ≥ trigger+blend: IK-driven disruption
        │
        ▼  (joint targets)
PD Controller → MuJoCo Physics
        │
        ▼
ISO15066Wrapper (samples forces at every sub-step)
```

---

