## Phase 1: SMPL-H Asset Preparation (4-5 days)

#### [NEW] [smplh_human.xml](file:///Users/ayushpatel/Documents/FYP3/safety_bigym/safety_bigym/assets/smplh_human.xml)

**Skeleton:**
- 52-joint SMPL-H hierarchy (match AMASS joint ordering exactly)
- Actuated joints with position control (`<joint>` + `<actuator>`)
- Height-scalable via `<default>` classes for 5th-95th percentile

**Collision capsules with soft contact:**
```xml
<default class="human_collision">
  <geom type="capsule" 
        solref="0.02 1.0" 
        solimp="0.9 0.95 0.001"
        group="2"/>
</default>
```

**Body region annotations (for PFL):**
```xml
<geom name="forearm_L_col" class="human_collision" 
      user="iso_region:forearm pressure_area:0.001"/>
```

**Environment fixture tagging (for quasi-static detection):**
```xml
<!-- In environment XMLs, tag static surfaces -->
<geom name="counter_top" group="3" user="fixture:true"/>
```

