## Phase 3: PD-Controlled Human (3-4 days)

#### [NEW] [human_controller.py](file:///Users/ayushpatel/Documents/FYP3/safety_bigym/safety_bigym/human/human_controller.py)

**Motion blending at trigger time:**
```python
def step(self, t: float, scenario: ScenarioParams, robot_state: dict):
    trigger = scenario.trigger_time
    blend = 0.4  # seconds
    
    if t < trigger:
        targets = self._amass_targets(t)
    elif t < trigger + blend:
        alpha = (t - trigger) / blend
        targets = (1 - alpha) * self._amass_targets(t) + alpha * self._ik_targets(robot_state)
    else:
        targets = self._ik_targets(robot_state)
    
    self._pd_controller.set_targets(targets)
```

