## Phase 5: Parameterised Scenario Sampler (3-4 days)

#### [NEW] [scenario_sampler.py](file:///Users/ayushpatel/Documents/FYP3/safety_bigym/safety_bigym/scenarios/scenario_sampler.py)

**Parameter Space:**
| Parameter | Range |
|-----------|-------|
| `clip` | 50-100 AMASS clips |
| `disruption` | 5 types (see below) |
| `trigger_time` | 0.2 – 0.8 × episode |
| `speed_multiplier` | 0.5 – 2.0 |
| `approach_angle` | 0° – 360° |
| `target_body_part` | `hand`, `forearm`, `torso`, `head` |
| `human_height` | 5th – 95th percentile |

**5 Disruption Types:**
| Type | Behaviour |
|------|-----------|
| `incidental` | AMASS walk; path intersects workspace |
| `shared_goal` | IK reach toward object near robot goal |
| `direct` | IK tracks robot EE with lag + noise |
| `obstruction` | Walk into robot path, hold position |
| `random_perturbed` | AMASS + Gaussian noise on trajectory |

**Episode lifecycle:**
```python
def reset(self, seed: int):
    self.scenario = self.sampler.sample_scenario(seed)  # Reproducible
    self.human.load_clip(self.scenario.clip)
```

