## Phase 7: Integration + Debugging (3-4 days)

#### [NEW] [safety_env.py](file:///Users/ayushpatel/Documents/FYP3/safety_bigym/safety_bigym/envs/safety_env.py)

Wrapper environment that:
1. Wraps any bigym environment
2. Spawns SMPL-H human with sampled scenario on [reset()](file:///Users/ayushpatel/Documents/FYP3/bigym/bigym/bigym_env.py#392-407)
3. Steps human motion controller on each [step()](file:///Users/ayushpatel/Documents/FYP3/bigym/bigym/envs/reach_target.py#104-107)
4. Applies ISO 15066 monitoring at each sub-step

- End-to-end testing with N=100 scenarios
- Video generation for each disruption type

