## Verification

```bash
# Phase 2 early check (before full library)
python scripts/preview_single_amass_clip.py --clip CMU/01/01_01.npz

# Unit tests
pytest tests/test_amass_loader.py -v
pytest tests/test_scenario_sampler.py -v
pytest tests/test_iso15066_wrapper.py -v

# Coverage: N=1000 scenarios, stratified reports
python scripts/run_coverage_eval.py --n 1000 --output results/
```

**Known limitation:** If physics sub-step rate is lower than impact duration, peak transient forces may be underestimated. Document and recommend running at 500Hz+ physics for accurate PFL measurement.
